Package searchfilterpkg

Class SearchFilterManager

java.lang.Object
searchfilterpkg.SearchFilterManager
public class SearchFilterManager extends Object
Used to store the types of search filters. Purpose is to call the filter function of the search filters.

      public ArrayList<String> filter(String nameOfFilter, String filterOption, ArrayList<String> campList)

      filterOption - Data used to filter the list (e.g. The name of location or the date of camp).

      Returns:
